      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is a solid, functional choice for anyone needing dependable transportation without the premium price tag! While it shows some clear signs of its journey through life\u2014including some cosmetic wear and tear and mechanical items that will need attention down the road\u2014it remains a practical option for your daily commute. It's a hardworking car ready for its next chapter with a owner who appreciates honest value!",
