      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in stunning, showroom-quality condition\u2014I've babied it from day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garaged, kept spotless, and drives like a charm. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and turns heads everywhere it goes, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
