    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a linear 8,000 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential, ensuring superlative mechanical grip. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service, addressing critical E46 weak points. The factory suspension geometry remains precise, providing the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance that defined this era of M-division performance. With original paint depth and a flawless interior, this is a turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
